name: Fallen Portal
Lore: 'Jabba ordered the two-meter thick door to keep the rancor in. He never thought it would be the instrument of the rancor''s demise.',
Text: 'Target one creature or up to two characters present that just initiated an attack or battle against you at Back Door, Rancor Pit, Tatooine: Jabba''s Palace or any docking bay. Draw destiny. Target(s) immediately lost if destiny +2 > total defense value.',
